metadata.name: Feel the Chlorophyll
metadata.description:
She walked alone in the summer garden

She had fiery red hair gleaming in the April sunlight

She was staring at the white sky through her blue eyes
This endless garden was her dream

She woke up and smelled chlorophyll and said it was unfortunate

"I want to keep dreaming"

This work is in the series Oxygen, it talk about dreams extravagance of mind and depict the daily life of various original character people in Anime-art style drawing by travenerd.

It will be dropped 12 pieces in the series in a different story.

You can own full right of art illust-design legally for commercial purposes.

Special for Collectors
If you collect 3 items in this collection, you will get a special image that combines all 3 characters as a special illustration as a gift (free) from travenerd.

Size : 700x700px in 300dpi
